com.adobe.cq.social.activitystreams.listener.api

Interface ActivityStreamProviderExtension


  • public interface ActivityStreamProviderExtension
    Stream provider extension. An stream provider extension can add custom properties to an activity, or veto an event so that no activity is generated for that event.
